    Course
    The Course class stores attributes of a single course, that belongs to a CourseEntry.

    The CourseEntry class stores all course entries that belong to a Module.

    This class is the super class of several Entry related subclasses.

    This class is the representation of a single Module.
    ModuleAdministration  
    SelfStudy
